header.info: A very active sheep with cute green horns.[br][br]Lots of changes from the original stray sheep.[br]Gus plays sounds, has all the old animations, and has plenty of new/custom animations, including many uncommon and rare ones![br](Best viewed with only one monitor.)[br][br]6.5 Changes:[br]Many bug fixes.[br]Animation/spawn improvements.[br]Improved King Sheep jumps.[br]King Sheep spawns more sheep.[br][br]Thanks for using![br]You can send feedback to[br]greenstraysheep@gmail.com
